---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Changelog -- 24K Labs">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header__glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-header__badge">Updates</span>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Changelog</h1>
      <p class="page-header__desc">What we shipped and when.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section--sm">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="timeline">

        <div class="timeline-entry reveal">
          <div class="timeline-date">April 2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-content card">
            <h3>24klabs.ai Website Launch</h3>
            <p>Full multi-page website live on Cloudflare Pages. API moved to Railway for 24/7 uptime. Product pages, developer docs, quickstart guide, x402 directory, and community hub.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry reveal">
          <div class="timeline-date">March 2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-content card">
            <h3>6 AI Services Live</h3>
            <p>All six code analysis endpoints operational with x402 payments on Base L2. Explain, debug, review, security audit, automation scripts, and MCP blueprints.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry reveal">
          <div class="timeline-date">March 2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-content card">
            <h3>x402 Payment Integration</h3>
            <p>Coinbase x402 SDK integrated. USDC payments on Base L2 with on-chain verification via facilitator. Payment is authentication -- no API keys needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry reveal">
          <div class="timeline-date">March 2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-content card">
            <h3>Bazaar Discovery</h3>
            <p>Agent discovery endpoints live at /.well-known/x402.json and /discovery/resources. AI agents can now find, evaluate, and pay for 24K Labs services autonomously.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="timeline-entry reveal">
          <div class="timeline-date">March 2026</div>
          <div class="timeline-content card">
            <h3>24K Labs Founded</h3>
            <p>Company founded in Philadelphia. First API endpoint deployed. Vision: AI code services paid via open payment protocols.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .timeline {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
  }
  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: var(--border);
  }
  .timeline-entry {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .timeline-entry::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -37px;
    top: 8px;
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gold);
    border: 2px solid var(--bg);
  }
  .timeline-date {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .timeline-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .timeline-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
